# Changelog

To install unreleased versions of a workspace package, see [developmental
releases](https://django-search-query.git-pull.com/quickstart.html#developmental-releases).

The workspace ships two packages -- `django-search-query` and
`django-admin-search-query` -- that version and release independently. Both
share this changelog; each release section names its package and version.

